FBIS4-61317 "drsov087_t_94010" FBIS-SOV-94-087 Daily Report 4 May 1994 BALTIC STATES Estonia Liberal Democratic Official Denounces `Baltic Fascism' Liberal Democratic Official Denounces `Baltic Fascism' WS0405140994 Tallinn ETA in English 0753 GMT 4 May 94 WS0405140994 Tallinn ETA English BFN [From "News Bulletin" No. 85/94] [Text] Representative of the Russian Liberal Democrats in Estonia Pyotr Rozhok has demanded economic sanctions against "Baltic Fascism" in a newspaper of their party. He calls for the Russian parliament to ban the export of oil products, metal, gas, energy resources and food to Estonia in order to "promote respect for Russia."
